OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773238281
OL,3,CCouncil urged to rethink after banning
OL,4,Cpub's free 'taxi service'
OL,6,FA pub landlord in Kent who was banned
OL,7,Ffrom giving his regulars a free ride
OL,8,Fhome says he's been overwhelmed by
OL,9,Fsupport from the public.
OL,11,FPaul Hartfield, who runs The Flying
OL,12,FHorse in Smarden, started offering
OL,13,Fcustomers a lift home at the end of
OL,14,Fthe night until the service was
OL,15,Fstopped by Ashford Borough Council.
OL,17,FCouncil officials say any transport
OL,18,Fservice must meet basic legal and
OL,19,Fsafety standards.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
