PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773238281
OL,3,CCouncil urged to rethink after banning
OL,4,Cpub's free 'taxi service'
OL,6,FMr Hartfield does not charge his
OL,7,Fregulars a fare but instead asks for
OL,8,Fan optional donation to charity.
OL,10,FHe said: "A lot of the older customers
OL,11,Fcome down on a Friday and they have to
OL,12,Fwalk home in the dark. There is
OL,13,Fpavements here at the moment but there
OL,14,Fis loads of lanes there isn't any
OL,15,Fpavements, no street lights and they
OL,16,Fcan come out on a Friday and know that
OL,17,Fthey will get home safely at ten
OL,18,Fo'clock when they want to."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
