FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773238281
OL,3,CCouncil urged to rethink after banning
OL,4,Cpub's free 'taxi service'
OL,6,FAshford Borough Council (ABC) has
OL,7,Fbanned the operation because Mr
OL,8,FHartfield does not have a private hire
OL,9,Fvehicle licence.
OL,11,FMr Hartfield added: "I don't think I
OL,12,Fneed a license to take my friends
OL,13,Fhome, anyone else could do it in a car
OL,14,Fso why can't I?"
OL,16,F"I don't want people to drink and
OL,17,Fdrive. All I am doing really is taking
OL,18,Fmy friends home after they've had a
OL,19,Fgood nights drink."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
