OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773238281
OL,3,CCouncil urged to rethink after banning
OL,4,Cpub's free 'taxi service'
OL,6,FSo far, Mr Hartfield has raised around
OL,7,F#700 for the Motor Neurone Disease
OL,8,FAssociation in donations since
OL,9,Fstarting the lifts in December.
OL,11,FOne regular at The Flying Horse said:
OL,12,F"It's not a pub cab scheme, it is a
OL,13,Fprivate car which happens to be a cab
OL,14,Fwhich Paul drives and takes people
OL,15,Fhome, so I think the ABC have had a
OL,16,Fcomplete misinterpretation of the
OL,17,Flegislation and applied it
OL,18,Fincorrectly."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
