PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773238281
OL,3,CCouncil urged to rethink after banning
OL,4,Cpub's free 'taxi service'
OL,6,FKatie Lam, the Conservative MP for
OL,7,FWeald of Kent, is calling on Ashford
OL,8,FBorough Council to use existing powers
OL,9,Fof exemption.
OL,11,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for the
OL,12,Fcouncil said: "We recognise the good
OL,13,Fintentions behind the service but we
OL,14,Falso have a responsibility to apply
OL,15,Fthe law fairly and consistently, with
OL,16,Fpublic safety remaining our priority."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
