PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773238281
OL,3,CCouncil urged to rethink after banning
OL,4,Cpub's free 'taxi service'
OL,6,F"The council's approach to licensing
OL,7,Fis not about being heavyhanded, but
OL,8,Fabout making sure that any transport
OL,9,Fservice operating locally meets the
OL,10,Fbasic legal and safety standards."
